    <h1>Three Good Things</h1>

<p>
  Since July 2022 I've tried to make a habit of noting three good things
  that have happened throughout the day. This has done good for my mental
  health, and serves as a nice little diary of my life too!
</p>

<p>
  I noted three good things on {{ len . }} days so far!
</p>

<p>
  This page is formatted as a <a target="_blank" href="https://journal.miso.town/">HTML journal</a>, a cool format designed for syndication and micro-blogging.
  You can get a feed from m15o's website &mdash; and I'm working on a Go implementation for this site too!
</p>

{{ range . }}
<article id="{{ .Title }}">
<h2>{{ .Title }}</h2>

<ol>
  <li>{{ .First }}</li>
  <li>{{ .Second }}</li>
  <li>{{ .Third }}</li>
</ol>
</article>
{{ end }}

